title: 1927
subtitle: 新的一年
on-arrival: old_republic = pro_republic; {!
// see post_event.scene.dry for changes.
Q.economic_growth += 5.1;
Q.unemployed -= 2;
Q.inflation -= 0.8;
if (Q.upper_tax_rates < 0) {
    Q.unemployed -= 1.1;
    Q.economic_growth += 2.5;
    Q.inflation += 0.2;
}
if (Q.lower_tax_rates < 0) {
    Q.unemployed -= 1.1;
    Q.economic_growth += 2.5;
    Q.inflation += 0.2;
}
Q.budget += 1;
!}
tags: event
view-if: year = 1927 and month = 1
priority: 2
max-visits: 1

新的一年开始了。在现任与前任政府的刺激政策推动下，经济正开始从去年的衰退中复苏。